---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Hotel" description="몽환적이고 평온한 숙소에서의 특별한 하루를 소개합니다." />
		<style>
			:where(html, body) { overflow-x: hidden; }
			main.page { width: 100%; max-width: 100%; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

			.hero {
				position: relative;
				min-height: 100svh;
				display: grid;
				place-items: center;
				place-content: center;
				padding: 6vh 1rem;
				background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.45), rgba(0,0,0,0.35)), url('/hotel1.png') center / cover no-repeat;
				color: #fff;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			.hero-inner {
				width: min(720px, calc(100% - 2rem)); max-width: 100%; padding: 2.25em 1.5em; text-align: center; margin: 0 auto;
				border-radius: 16px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
				box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
				backdrop-filter: blur(6px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
				border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
			}
			h1 { margin: 0 0 .5em 0; font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.75rem); letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
			p.lead { margin: 0.2em auto 1em auto; max-width: 44ch; font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2.2vw, 1.0625rem); line-height: 1.9; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); }
			.meta { margin-top: 1.25em; font-size: .95rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); }
			.meta a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); text-decoration: underline; }
			.meta a:hover { color: #fff; }
			@supports(padding: max(0px)) {
				.hero-inner { padding-bottom: max(1.5em, env(safe-area-inset-bottom)); }
			}
			/* 모바일에서 배경 이미지가 잘리지 않도록 전체(Contain) 표시 */
			@media (max-width: 700px) {
				.hero {
					background-position: center, center;
					background-size: auto, contain;
					background-repeat: no-repeat, no-repeat;
				}
			}
			@media (max-width: 480px) {
				.hero { padding: 5vh 0.75rem; }
				.hero-inner { width: min(640px, calc(100% - 1.5rem)); padding: 1.75em 1.25em; }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="page">
			<section class="hero">
				<div class="hero-inner">
					<h1>Hotel · 머무는 순간이 여행이 되는 곳</h1>
					<p class="lead">아름답고 평온한 공간에서, 라운드의 여운을 길게 즐겨보세요.</p>
					<p class="lead">자연과 어우러진 뷰, 깊은 수면을 돕는 조도, 포근한 텍스타일.</p>
					<p class="lead">미니멀한 디자인 속 디테일, 가벼운 스낵과 웰컴 드링크.</p>
					<p class="lead">라운지의 잔잔한 플레이리스트와 향기로운 어메니티.</p>
					<p class="lead">머무는 시간 자체가 힐링이 되는, 우리만의 숙소 셀렉션.</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html> 